1.下載BLAT
https://www.blat.net/

2.安裝BLAT
Command = '"' |  [Blat folder path] | '" -install ' | [SMTP IP] | ' ' | [Sender];

3.寄信Command line:
Command = '"' |  [Blat folder path]  | '" ' 
              |  [email Body]
              | ' -t "'           |  [Recipient]
              | '" -f "'          |  [Sender]
              | '" -subject '     | '"' | [Subject] | '"' 
              | ' -attach '       | '"' | [Attach]  | '"'
              |  ' -html ';
